urlLink Military Strategy As Get Rich Scheme :: War, Politics, Culture ::  : "Commentary:ï¿½Military Strategy As Get Rich Scheme    What the Bush Administration calls a military strategy is really a commercial venture, one increasingly dangerous for America and the world.  By Mick Youther  A recent newspaper story from Crawford, Texas said that President Bush, Vice President Cheney and Secretary of Defense Rumsfeld had just had a meeting on military strategy. That was a surprise to me because I thought they had already perfected their military strategy -- Bush starts a war, handpicked corporations are paid to do everything except the fighting and dying, and then Cheney%u2019s old company is paid big money to clean up the mess. "